@SmartBets_HostAddress = http://localhost:5160
@ApiKey = your-api-key-here

### Health
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/ping
Accept: application/json

### Countries sync
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/countries/sync
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Leagues sync
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/leagues/sync
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Preload current leagues in core-data mode
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/preload/run
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Preload one season in small batch, skipping recently synced features
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/preload/run?season=2025&maxLeagues=5&minMinutesSinceLastSync=180&stopOnRateLimit=true
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Preload one season in core mode including pre-match odds
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/preload/run?season=2025&maxLeagues=5&includeOdds=true&stopOnRateLimit=true
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Historical bootstrap for frozen seasons, excluding the automation window
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/preload/historical?fromSeason=2023&toSeason=2024&maxLeagueSeasons=20&includeOdds=false&excludeAutomationWindow=true
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Historical bootstrap with pre-match odds snapshots
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/preload/historical?fromSeason=2023&toSeason=2024&maxLeagueSeasons=10&includeOdds=true&force=false
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Force preload one season in small batch
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/preload/run?season=2025&maxLeagues=5&force=true&minMinutesSinceLastSync=0
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Teams sync for one league-season
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/teams/sync?leagueId=39&season=2025
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Full fixtures sync for one league-season
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/sync?leagueId=39&season=2025
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Upcoming fixtures sync for one league-season
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/sync-upcoming?leagueId=39&season=2025
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Lightweight live-status sync for active supported leagues
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/sync-live-status?activeOnly=true
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Lightweight live-status sync for one league
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/sync-live-status?leagueId=39
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Match winner odds sync for one league-season
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/odds/sync?leagueId=39&season=2025&marketName=Match%20Winner
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Sync bookmaker reference catalog from API-Football
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/bookmakers/sync-reference
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Rebuild odds analytics from local snapshots only
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/odds/analytics/rebuild?leagueId=39&season=2025&marketName=Match%20Winner
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Standings sync for one league-season
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/standings/sync?leagueId=39&season=2025
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Legacy fixtures list with filters
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures?leagueId=39&season=2025&state=Upcoming&direction=asc
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Paged fixtures query for frontend
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/query?leagueId=39&season=2025&state=Finished&from=2025-08-01&to=2025-08-31&page=1&pageSize=20&direction=desc
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Team-centric fixtures query using API team id
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/query?teamId=33&state=Live&page=1&pageSize=10
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Fixture detail by API fixture id
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/123456?marketName=Match%20Winner
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Match-center sync for one fixture
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/123456/sync-match-center?includePlayers=true&force=false
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Live match-center sync batch
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/sync-live-match-center?leagueId=39&season=2025&maxFixtures=10&includePlayers=false&force=false
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Sync live bet types
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/odds/live-bets/sync
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Get live bet types
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/odds/live-bets
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Sync live odds for one live fixture
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/odds/live/sync?fixtureId=123456
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Sync live odds for one league and live bet type
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/odds/live/sync?leagueId=39&betId=1
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Read stored live odds by API fixture id
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/odds/live?apiFixtureId=123456&betId=1&latestOnly=true
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Read stored live odds through fixture route
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/123456/odds/live?betId=1&latestOnly=true
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Preview sync for one fixture
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/123456/sync-preview?force=false
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

