### Add one supported league
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/admin/supported-leagues
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "leagueApiId": 39,
  "season": 2025,
  "isActive": true,
  "priority": 10
}

### Bulk add or update supported leagues
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/admin/supported-leagues/bulk
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "leagueApiId": 1,
      "season": 2026,
      "isActive": true,
      "priority": 1
    },
    {
      "leagueApiId": 140,
      "season": 2025,
      "isActive": true,
      "priority": 10
    },
    {
      "leagueApiId": 39,
      "season": 2025,
      "isActive": true,
      "priority": 20
    }
  ]
}
